biography: Prof. Dr. Michael Feindt is the brain behind Blue Yonder GmbH. His NeuroBayes algorithm was developed during his many years of scientific research at CERN. Michael is also a professor at the Karlsruhe Institute of Technology (KIT), Germany, and a lecturer at the Data Science Academy.
